title: Mega Billionaire, Will Packer Interview, Midterm Elections, World Series, Rae Carruth, Closing Remarks and more.
itunes:title: Mega Billionaire, Will Packer Interview, Midterm Elections, World Series, Rae Carruth, Closing Remarks and more.
description:
Who will win the money? Will Packer stops by the show to talk about Ready To Love. Midterm elections are upon us and who will win? MLB World Series is here and it's LA vs Boston. Former Carolina Panther Rae Carruth is released from prison. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog has a message for Nephew Tommy and more.
